name: YOLO Corgi
description:
The YOLO Corgi game is a racing 2D game. The purpose of the corgi is to pass the obstacle and meet the cabbage again. An example of an obstacle is the bomber boxes that destroy the mountain and humans who want to ruin our environment.

Once upon a time...

Humans destroy the environment around the world. 

So, the punisher name 'Corgi the YOLO' have come to the land of humans, 

To protect the earth. Protect the family, and protect Garbage.

Have fun !
